                "image_link": "https://spcdn.shortpixel.ai/spio/ret_img,q_cdnize,to_auto,s_webp:avif/visuelle.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Koto-x-De-extinction-_-Website-Laptop-2000x1125-copy.webp",
                "caption": ""
            },
            {
                "paragraph": "Koto introduces a name and brand for the launch of De-extinction , a company saying no to single-use plastics through eco-friendly alternatives—ranging from tableware and cutlery to food packaging. Rooted in a rebellious but playful ethos, De-extinction stands as a proactive force against waste. Dinosaurs, witnesses to their own extinction, emerge as compelling advocates for planet and ecosystem preservation, igniting the ‘De-extinction movement’."
            },
            {
                "paragraph": "Koto’s visual language centers around a playful dinosaur motif, an unexpected yet familiar warning against extinction amid waste threats. This distinctive style harmonizes expressiveness and rebellion, differentiating from competitors while addressing planetary conservation’s importance."
            },
